#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid "Pirates - Bounty APM"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid ""
"[[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]] combined with [[Proud Privateer||122520]] "
"gives you lots of gold to hit more of your setup.  Cycle [[Tranquil "
"Meditative||119942]], or spell buff Chromadrakes with Brann for spell "
"scaling to make your bounties buff more. You also want to cycle every single"
" free card ([[Refreshing Anomaly||64042]]) and [[Roving Sailor||130705]] so "
"you stay infinite. You may want to scale using [[Brazen Buccaneer||130703]] "
"+ [[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]] as well. ADVANCED PLAYERS: After you're "
"infinite, think about the highest possible scaling from your spot. Options "
"include Ship Jumper Pivot ([[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] + [[Titus "
"Rivendare||97408]]) or [[Fire-forged Evoker||120301]] Pivot ([[Persistent "
"Poet||108463]] + [[Nightbane, Ignited||110088]])"
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid ""
"Bounty Generation ([[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]]) + [[Proud "
"Privateer||122520]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid ""
"Midgame Bounties ([[Bigwig Bandit||122179]]/[[Lost City Looter||122175]])"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid "Bounties generate gold and stats"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid "Demons - Shop Buff"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid ""
"Scale your shop somehow, usually it's through [[Shadowdancer||120662]], "
"[[Felemental||97553]], or [[Consummate Conqueror||130079]]. Then, add "
"fodders to your shop to capture the buffed minions in shop. Typically you "
"have an economy setup with [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + damage rewinder "
"([[Ashen Corruptor||121687]]) which allows you to cycle a lot of cards. "
"Every card you cycle will add a lot of fodders to eat because of [[Twisted "
"Wrathguard||130662]]. There's another line where you can add fodders to your"
" shop using [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Laboratory Assistant||130075]]."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid ""
"Buffed Shop ([[Shadowdancer||120662]]) + [[Ashen Corruptor||121687]] + "
"[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid ""
"[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]\n"
"Demon midgame ([[Woodland Defiler||130076]])"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid "Scale and consume shop"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/81/
msgid "Elementals - Shop Buff/Spells"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/81/
msgid ""
"First, buff the shop. This is usually done by having [[Living "
"Azerite||107939]], but [[Air Revenant||126173]] works as well. [[Brann "
"Bronzebeard||96786]] + [[Lantern Lava||122650]] gives you all the economy "
"you need. Keep a good battlecry elemental on your board every turn, usually "
"[[Refreshing Anomaly||64042]] for money and [[Leyline Surfacer||130294]] for"
" stats. Double the effect of the [[Arcane Absorption||130311]] you get from "
"Leyline using [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]]. In the endgame, scale up "
"[[Wildfire Elemental||64189]]."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/81/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + [[Lantern Lava||122650]] good economy"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/81/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/81/
msgid "Make big units in shop to scale."
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/48/
msgid "Beasts - Stegodon"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/48/
msgid ""
"Initially attack with your [[Stomping Stegodon||122286]]. Make sure that you"
" have a taunted [[Sewer Rat||70790]] or any multi-hit taunt to soak some "
"attacks. Then, the next things to attack should be [[Manasaber||98831]] then"
" [[Sewer Lord||130996]] because this fills out the board with a lot of "
"taunts that protect your Poultron. Every 4 things that die will give your "
"board insane rallys because your Poultron's will attack and swing with all "
"the combined rallies. Also don't reborn your Stegodon!! With [[Sprightly "
"Scarab||108909]], you want to first reborn your Poultrons, then the "
"Manasabers and Sewer Lord. Comp is much better if your Poultron is golden."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/48/
msgid "[[Stomping Stegodon||122286]] + Beasts ([[Manasaber||98831]])"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/48/
msgid "[[Stomping Stegodon||122286]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/48/
msgid "Exponentially scale attack with rally"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid "Beasts - Summons"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid ""
"[[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] + [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] and [[Titus"
" Rivendare||97408]] gives a huge aura affect to all beasts you summon. "
"Usually, you want to taunt and reborn the Goldrinn so the Macaw always procs"
" it and it always dies. [[Sewer Lord||130996]] is the best summon beast to "
"run in this comp."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid ""
"[[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] + beast summons ([[Sewer Lord||130996]])"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid "[[Titus Rivendare||97408]] + [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid "Scale summoned beasts in combat"
msgstr ""
